7
00:01:36,250 --> 00:01:38,208
MAROC

8
00:02:12,541 --> 00:02:13,375
Ça va ?

9
00:02:13,458 --> 00:02:15,416
Oui.

10
00:02:16,375 --> 00:02:17,333
